lead_paragraph: When Wake Forest fans look back at 2016, perhaps they will remember an exciting victory in the Military Bowl as the culmination of the team's first winning season in eight years.

headline.print_headline: Wake Forest Survives Temple Rally to Win Military Bowl 34-26
